&lt;p&gt;I&amp;rsquo;m using Cloudflare as CDN for api.davidxiao.me, so I went on to the Cloudflare portal and updated the &amp;ldquo;Minimum TLS Version&amp;rdquo; to &amp;ldquo;TLS 1.2&amp;rdquo;.&lt;/p&gt;





  
  











